  title: "Groundhog vs. mole holes: how to tell the difference",
  description:
    "Use hole size, soil patterns, and surface tunnels to quickly identify whether you’re dealing with a groundhog burrow or mole activity—plus what to do next.",
  canonical: "https://openinfohub.net/pest-control/groundhog-vs-mole-holes/",
  updated: "2026-02-02",
